714311f-a.title: Manhattan: 71st Street (East) - York Avenue
714311f-a.text:
501-7 East 71st Street, at N.E. corner of York avenue.
In the foreground is the excavation for the Cornklf Medical College--
New York Hospital.
July 31,1930.

724902f-a.title: Manhattan: York Avenue - 71st Street
724902f-a.text:
York Avenue (Avenue A), east side, from 71st to 74th Streets, showing
the new P. Lorillard factory, erected around 1923 where the old
Charles C. Clausen Malt House stood since around 1885.
September 15, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
